Revision history for Crypt-Liboqs-Sign

0.01    2026-03-07
        - Initial release
        - Drop-in replacement for Crypt::PQClean::Sign
        - Supports all liboqs signature algorithms: Falcon, ML-DSA,
          SPHINCS+, Dilithium, MAYO, CROSS, OV, SNOVA
        - Backward-compatible function names with Crypt::PQClean::Sign
        - Dynamic function generation for all enabled algorithms
